            </div>
            <a href="https://www.joinblvd.com/b/3fdd50b8-7139-46c6-b272-20a94ddbbf3d/widget" data-booking-trigger="boulevard" class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-[#F3A2A7] text-white font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition self-center" data-t-es="Agendar Ahora" data-t-en="Book Now">Agendar Ahora</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden min-h-[260px] text-white">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/img/services/PRP-face.jpg');"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/55"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10 p-6 flex flex-col h-full text-center">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl mb-2" data-t-es="MICRONEEDLING WITH PRP" data-t-en="MICRONEEDLING WITH PRP">MICRONEEDLING WITH PRP</h3>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-white/90 mb-4">
                <span class="flex-1 h-px bg-white/70"></span>
                <span data-t-es="$425 por tratamiento" data-t-en="$425 per treatment">$425 por tratamiento</span>
                <span class="flex-1 h-px bg-white/70"></span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/90 mb-3" data-t-es="Complemento de pecho – $99" data-t-en="Chest Add-On – $99">Complemento de pecho – $99</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/90 mb-4" data-t-es="Potencia tus resultados con PRP (“Oro Líquido”) para acelerar la recuperación y aumentar la producción de colágeno." data-t-en="Enhance your microneedling results with PRP (“Liquid Gold”) to speed healing and boost collagen production.">Potencia tus resultados con PRP (“Oro Líquido”) para acelerar la recuperación y aumentar la producción de colágeno.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="https://www.joinblvd.com/b/3fdd50b8-7139-46c6-b272-20a94ddbbf3d/widget" data-booking-trigger="boulevard" class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-[#F3A2A7] text-white font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition self-center" data-t-es="Agendar Ahora" data-t-en="Book Now">Agendar Ahora</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden min-h-[260px] text-white">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/img/services/Piel-laser-general.jpg');"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/55"></div>
          <div class="relative z-10 p-6 flex flex-col h-full text-center">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl mb-2" data-t-es="RF MICRONEEDLING" data-t-en="RF MICRONEEDLING">RF MICRONEEDLING</h3>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-sm text-white/90 mb-4">
                <span class="flex-1 h-px bg-white/70"></span>
                <span data-t-es="$525 por tratamiento" data-t-en="$525 per treatment">$525 por tratamiento</span>
                <span class="flex-1 h-px bg-white/70"></span>
              </div>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/90 mb-3" data-t-es="Complemento de pecho – $99" data-t-en="Chest Add-On – $99">Complemento de pecho – $99</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-white/90 mb-4" data-t-es="Combina microneedling con energía de radiofrecuencia para tensar la piel y mejorar la elasticidad en profundidad." data-t-en="Combines microneedling with gentle radiofrequency energy to tighten skin and improve elasticity at a deeper level.">Combina microneedling con energía de radiofrecuencia para tensar la piel y mejorar la elasticidad en profundidad.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="https://www.joinblvd.com/b/3fdd50b8-7139-46c6-b272-20a94ddbbf3d/widget" data-booking-trigger="boulevard" class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-[#F3A2A7] text-white font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition self-center" data-t-es="Agendar Ahora" data-t-en="Book Now">Agendar Ahora</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mt-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden min-h-[260px] text-white">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/img/services/PRP-decollet.jpg');"></div>
